About this hotel

This laid-back hotel in a traditional riad is 3 km from Majorelle Garden, and 5 km from both the lively Jemaa el-Fnaa square and the 12th-century Koutoubia Mosque.

    About this hotel

    This laid-back hotel in a traditional riad is 3 km from Majorelle Garden, and 5 km from both the lively Jemaa el-Fnaa square and the 12th-century Koutoubia Mosque. …

    Warm rooms offer flat-screen TVs, Wi-Fi access and en suite bathrooms, as well as minifridges, safes and balconies. Some come with sitting areas.

    Parking is complimentary. Other amenities consist of a restaurant and an outdoor pool with sunloungers. Breakfast and massage services are available, as is an airport shuttle.
